{"sta":1,"data":{"subTitle":"动画的暂停与播放","content":"<p>SVG animation中是有内置的API可以暂停和启动动画的。语法为：</p><div><pre><span>// svg指当前svg DOM元素\n// 暂停</span>\nsvg.pauseAnimations();\n\n<span>// 重启动</span>\nsvg.unpauseAnimations()\n</pre></div><p>例如下面这个马儿，点击就会暂停，再点就会重新运动。<br><svg width=\"320\" height=\"320\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" onclick=\"if (this.paused != true) { this.pauseAnimations(); this.paused = true; } else  { this.unpauseAnimations(); this.paused = false; }\"><g transform=\"rotate(332.451 160 160)\"><text font-family=\"microsoft yahei\" font-size=\"120\" y=\"160\" x=\"160\">马<animateTransform attributeName=\"transform\" begin=\"0s\" dur=\"10s\" type=\"rotate\" from=\"0 160 160\" to=\"360 160 160\" repeatCount=\"indefinite\"></animateTransform></text></g></svg></p>"}}